## CLI Interface

```bash
# Basic usage
python discover.py --city "Istanbul"

# With options
python discover.py --city "Istanbul" --max-posts 100 --skip-scrape --only-extract
```

### CLI Arguments

| Argument         | Required | Default | Description                                               |
| ---------------- | -------- | ------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| `--city`         | Yes      | —       | City name to research                                     |
| `--max-posts`    | No       | 100     | Max posts to pull per hashtag per platform                |
| `--skip-scrape`  | No       | false   | Skip scraping, run extraction on existing raw posts       |
| `--only-extract` | No       | false   | Only run LLM extraction + scoring on already-scraped data |
| `--reset`        | No       | false   | Clear all data for this city before running               |

