## Error Handling & Resilience

- **Checkpoint-based**: each step marks its work as done in the DB, so reruns skip completed work
- **Retry logic**: all API calls (Apify + OpenRouter) retry 3x with exponential backoff
- **Graceful failure**: if a single hashtag scrape fails, log and continue with the rest
- **Idempotent**: running the same city twice adds new data without duplicating existing posts
- **Progress logging**: print step-by-step progress to stdout (e.g., "Scraping hashtag 3/15: istanbulfoodie...")

